# Profile guardrails (narofitness)

Portable Ordia rules apply to all profiles. Domain constraints live in `narofitness-permanent-guardrails.mdc`. This file captures **profile operations** for `narofitness`.

## Product scope

- Product roots: `apps/` (blocked for orchestration sessions per `ordia.yaml`)
- Control roots: `docs/control/`, `docs/ordia/`, `.cursor/`, `AGENTS.md`, `ordia.yaml`
- Monorepo layout: `apps/api/` (FastAPI), `apps/desktop/` (Electron + Vite), `packaging/`, `scripts/`

## Commands and validation

- Closure gate: `npm run ordia:validate` → `ordia validate --project`
- Health check: `npm run ordia:doctor`
- Emit prompts: `npm run ordia:prompt -- emit --intent <ID> --task <TASK-ID>`
- Recovery bootstrap: `npm run ordia:prompt-recover`
- Task state: `npm run ordia:task-summary` / `npm run ordia:task-transition -- --task <ID> --status <STATUS>`
- Catalog: `docs/control/commands.catalog.json` + `docs/control/COMMANDS.md`

